Usage: gui_get_legend [-help]
                      -type {inst_density pin_density timing_map metal_density route_congestion temperature} [-display_range  | -value_range  | -show_legend_on_layout  | -legend_location  | -enable_min_value  | -enable_max_value ]

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
-display_range             # Get the display range (bool, optional)
-enable_max_value          # Get the state of the max value of display range
                           # (bool, optional)
-enable_min_value          # Get the state of the min value of display range
                           # (bool, optional)
-legend_location           # Get the location of legend (bool, optional)
-show_legend_on_layout     # Get the state of legend on layout (bool, optional)
-type {inst_density pin_density timing_map metal_density route_congestion temperature}
                           # Legend type (enum, required)
-value_range               # Get the value range (bool, optional)